th & Activities ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/health-activities/226396)\n## [Tonight's Weather Thu, May 21  ![](https://www.awxcdn.com/adc-assets/images/weathericons/v2a/12.svg) Showers this evening; otherwise, overcast and breezy **Lo: 15°** ![](https://www.awxcdn.com/adc-assets/images/weathericons/v2a/12.svg) Tomorrow: A couple of morning showers; otherwise, windy and cooler with considerable cloudiness **Hi: 17°** ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/weather-today/226396)\n## [ Current Weather  8:39 PM  ![](https://www.accuweather.com/images/weathericons/v2a/35.svg) 16°C RealFeel® 14°  Partly cloudy More Details Wind NNE 9 km/h Wind Gusts 15 km/h Air Quality Fair ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/current-weather/226396)\n## Tokyo Weather Radar\n[ ![Tokyo Weather Radar](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/weather-forecast/226396) Static Radar Temporarily Unavailable Thank you for your patience as we work to get everything up and running again. Refresh Page ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/weather-radar/226396)\n[ ![](https://www.awxcdn.com/adc-assets/images/components/maps/mapping-layers/realvue-satellite.jpg) Clouds ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/satellite/226396) [ ![](https://www.awxcdn.com/adc-assets/images/components/maps/mapping-layers/temperature.jpg) Temperature ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/current-weather-maps)\n## Hourly Weather\nChevron left\n[ 9 PM  ![](https://www.awxcdn.com/adc-assets/images/weathericons/v2a/12.svg) 17° 62% ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/hourly-weather-forecast/226396?hour=1779364800) [ 10 PM  ![](https://www.awxcdn.com/adc-assets/images/weathericons/v2a/12.svg) 17° 69% ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/hourly-weather-forecast/226396?hour=1779368400) [ 11 PM  ![](https://www.awxcdn.com/adc-assets/images/weathericons/v2a/12.svg) 17° 75% ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/hourly-weather-