=8) [ Fri 5/29 ![](https://www.awxcdn.com/adc-assets/images/weathericons/v2a/14.svg) 31° 21° Warm; a little afternoon rain ![](https://www.awxcdn.com/adc-assets/images/weathericons/v2a/33.svg) Clear and humid ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/daily-weather-forecast/226396?day=9) [ Sat 5/30 ![](https://www.awxcdn.com/adc-assets/images/weathericons/v2a/4.svg) 26° 19° A quick afternoon shower ![](https://www.awxcdn.com/adc-assets/images/weathericons/v2a/36.svg) A shower early; partly cloudy ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/daily-weather-forecast/226396?day=10)\n##  Sun & Moon \n![](https://www.accuweather.com/images/weathericons/v2a/1.svg) 14 hrs 11 mins\nRise 4:32 AM\nSet 6:43 PM\n![](https://www.accuweather.com/images/moon-phases/colored/light/WaxingCrescent.svg) Waxing Crescent\nRise 8:37 AM\nSet 11:26 PM\n## [Air Quality See More Air Quality Fair The air quality is generally acceptable for most individuals. However, sensitive groups may experience minor to moderate symptoms from long-term exposure.  ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/air-quality-index/226396)\n##  Allergy Outlook \n[See All](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/health-activities/226396)\n[ Dust & Dander High Data is not supported in this location ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/allergies-weather/226396?name=dust-dander)\nTop Stories\n[ Severe Weather Severe storms with damaging winds to focus on central US 1 hour ago ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/severe-weather/severe-storms-with-damaging-winds-to-focus-on-central-us/1892708) [ Weather Forecasts Northeast temps to crash 25° to 50°F ahead of Memorial Day weekend 1 hour ago ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/weather-forecasts/northeasts-temperatures-to-crash-25-50-degrees-ahead-of-memorial-day-weekend/1892923) [ Weather News Man rescued from Santa Rosa Island; SOS written on charred landscape 20 hours ago ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/weather-news/man-rescued-from-santa-rosa-